race.comment: GREEN RUN (4) is building towards a win, but he can't buy a decent barrier. Covered plenty of ground in the run when third over 1600m at Coonamble. Finds a weaker contest and goes close. SAINT PHILOMENA (7) good win at Dubbo two back before rising in class when fifth over 1600m at Coonamble. Deep into the prep and expect to see her race closer to the speed. Among the leading chances. ALWAYS FIORENTE (8) all three wins have come at this distance and should get his desired tempo today. Winning rider sticks with the claim and anywhere near his best can win this. AUTUMN SONG (1) indicated he was near his top when gripping on late to finish second over 1600m at Coonamble. Stiff's 3kg claim keeps him in the mix. SANZENO (5) third-up for this and expecting a better effort with the big weight drop.
